Name: Don't Crash - The Zombie Game
About the game: WARNING THIS GAME CRASHES WHEN YOU DIE! IT'S THE POINT OF THE GAME! THIS IS A WORK IN PROGRESS GAME! Welcome to the second installment of the 'Don't Crash' game series! Game features 'endless' Zombie and Soldier combat, 4 levels! As well as shotgun, pistols, assault rifles, and knives. Key Features: 1. Game Crashes When You Die 2. Zombie and Soldier AI With Cover and Footstep Listening 3. First Person Shooting 4. Several Weapons, grenades, rifles, pistols, shotgun, RPG Launcher, and a knife. 5. Four Levels. Warehouse, Hospital, Mansion, and Bunker. 6. Score System 7. Hidden Easter Eggs
